    <title>Diffraction Gratings</title>
    <p>Diffraction gratings are an optical tool that are made up of many many slits side-by-side, sometimes thousands of slits per millimeter, and allow for the diffraction of light. Diffraction gratings work through multiple-slit interference.</p>
